---
title: "HN collect flow (current / Implemented)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI as CLI entry (hn_agent / main)
    participant Col as collectors.tavily
    participant API as Tavily API
    participant Disp as display

    alt pulse.agents.hn_agent
        User->>CLI: uv run python -m pulse.agents.hn_agent
    else pulse.main
        User->>CLI: uv run python -m pulse.main
    end
    CLI->>CLI: fetch_hn_articles()
    CLI->>Col: search_articles(query, Source.HACKER_NEWS)
    Col->>API: TavilyClient.search("AI LLM site:news.ycombinator.com")
    API-->>Col: raw results[]
    Col->>Col: parse_tavily_results() → ArticleList
    Col-->>CLI: ArticleList
    CLI->>Disp: warn_if_below_minimum(articles, min_count)
    CLI->>Disp: print_articles(articles)
    Disp-->>User: N articles (title, url, score, summary)
